<br>
So I guess I am so wrong and need to do more research... it is well worth your time to get 30-50 people, deal with the politics of the RTA, and spend 2-12 hours in fear dealing with possibly massive wipeouts and long CR to get that awesome TV armor, instead of getting a group or soloing or spending some time in EC to get those armors listed above.  I am so sorry, I was way off base.<br>
<br>
I know of people who have been on 20+ fear raids over 1-2 years who havent gotten a full suit.<br>
