So gain 13 ac, 11 str, roughly same HP (with stam vs hp), and less agi/dex/wis... by spending time for a few days to get a full suit of armor... or spend months on end countless hours, hassled, cr, death, hassles, loot disputes, rare drops... in Fear.<br>
<br>
THAT is my argument.  I could do this for other classes (with the exception of warrior) for most of its armor, and some classes come out a lot better than ranjur... like shaman.<br>
