if there is a FFA day on the calendar that hasn't been reserved, then why don't you guys go jump in the mix then? see what you're all about, test the water, dip your toe, have a blast, kill some fingers, train draco to your camp, collect 120 corpses of your favorite guildmates. because when you are inexperienced, THAT is what fear is all about my friends. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><P ALIGN="LEFT">

